// Wardley Map — Agentic mesh strategy

title: Setting up an agentic mesh
date: 2025-01-15
author: Architecture
scope: IS transformation towards cognitive automation
question: "Where to invest to enable the emergence of an agentic mesh?"
doctrine: context

stages: Genesis, Custom, Product, Commodity
legend

// Anchors
anchor Business
anchor Process Owner : III.2

// Visible layer: automated business processes
Automated business process : II.2 {
  asset: financial
  note: "The real value — still largely to be built"
}

// Ecosystem level
Agentic Mesh : I.7 >> II.5 {
  asset: tech
  color: #5DBEA3
  note: "Strategic target"
}

// Agents: different maturity levels depending on use cases
Decision agent : I.5 >> II.7 {
  type: build
  asset: tech
  color: #5DBEA3
  cost: "Variable per domain"
}

pipeline Decision agent {
  Prototype agent : I.5
  Application agent : II.3
  Agent-product : III.3
}

// Agentic engineering patterns and frameworks
Agentic engineering pattern : II.2 >> III.5 {
  type: build
  asset: tech
  note: "Code orchestration, feedback loops, observability"
}

// The dominant trap
Off-the-shelf agentic system : III.7 (buy) {
  asset: tech
  color: #F39C12
  note: "The shortcut temptation — natural language directives"
}

// Manifest / standards layer
Intent manifest : I.3 >> II.5 {
  type: build
  asset: tech
}

A2A / MCP protocols : II.5 >> III.5 {
  type: buy
  asset: social
}

// Governance
Automated governance : I.8 >> II.7 {
  type: build
  asset: social
  cost: "Organizational investment"
}

Domain ownership : II.3 {
  asset: human
  note: "New competency for business teams"
}

// Digital platform: the real MVP
Digital platform : II.8 >> III.5 {
  type: build
  asset: tech
  color: #3498DB
  cost: "Structural investment — value independent of agents"
  note: "THE real MVP"
}

Read API : III.2 >> III.7 {
  type: build
  asset: tech
}

Write API : III.0 >> III.7 {
  type: build
  asset: tech
}

// Infrastructure
LLM : III.5 (buy) {
  cost: "Variable cost, declining"
}

Cloud Infrastructure : IV.3 (buy)

Business data : III.5 {
  asset: tech
}

Existing IS : III.8 !!(tech,financial) {
  asset: tech
  cost: "70-80% of IT budget"
}

// Value chain
Business -> Automated business process
Process Owner -> Automated business process
Automated business process -> Agentic Mesh
Agentic Mesh -> Decision agent
Agentic Mesh -> Automated governance
Agentic Mesh -> Intent manifest
Agentic Mesh -> A2A / MCP protocols

Decision agent -> Agentic engineering pattern
Decision agent -> Domain ownership
Decision agent -> Intent manifest
Decision agent -> Digital platform
Decision agent -> LLM

Agentic engineering pattern -> LLM

Digital platform -> Read API
Digital platform -> Write API
Read API -> Business data
Write API -> Existing IS
Read API -> Existing IS
Business data -> Existing IS

LLM -> Cloud Infrastructure
Existing IS -> Cloud Infrastructure

// Groups by EVT
group Agent team (per domain) {
  team: settler
  color: #5DBEA3
  Decision agent
  Intent manifest
  Domain ownership
}

group Platform team {
  team: town-planner
  color: #3498DB
  Digital platform
  Read API
  Write API
  Agentic engineering pattern
}

group Governance cell {
  team: settler
  Automated governance
  A2A / MCP protocols
}

// Warnings — common traps
warning "NIH if we build what we can buy — but beware the real complexity of a production agent" on Off-the-shelf agentic system
warning "Strong temptation to start directly here — a shortcut that does not hold in production" on Off-the-shelf agentic system
warning "Legacy IS = major inertia for exposing read/write" on Existing IS
warning "Without a standardized manifest, no mesh is possible" on Intent manifest

// Strategic notes
note "The real MVP — delivers value BEFORE and WITHOUT agents" on Digital platform
note "POC here, then productization, then domain ownership" on Decision agent
note "Emerges naturally as agents multiply" on Agentic Mesh

// Climate signals
signal commoditization on LLM
signal commoditization on Cloud Infrastructure
signal accelerating on Off-the-shelf agentic system
signal co-evolution on Agentic engineering pattern
signal network-effects on Agentic Mesh
signal red-queen on Automated business process

// Gameplays
gameplay strangler-fig "Progressively expose legacy IS via the platform" on Existing IS
gameplay ILC "Platform as foundation, agent ecosystem per domain, pattern standardization" on Digital platform
gameplay land-grab "Establish the manifest as internal standard before fragmentation" on Intent manifest

